msgctxt "an8.84:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.84:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga "
msgstr "9. Mindfulness "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 84. Corasutta → mahācoraṅgasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Corasutta "
msgstr "84. A Master Thief "

# NOTE: BB’s “gets into trouble” is too weak. Elsewhere this term explictly means to be killed (pare hananti pariyāpādenti). Since “na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti” is a idiom meaning they’re going to die, and execution is the standard punishment for theft, it’s clearly the meaning here.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.84:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato mahācoro khippaṃ pariyāpajjati, na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a master thief with eight factors is soon executed, and doesn’t have long to live. "

msgctxt "an8.84:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.84:1.3"
msgid "Appaharantassa paharati, anavasesaṃ ādiyati, itthiṃ hanati, kumāriṃ dūseti, pabbajitaṃ vilumpati, rājakosaṃ vilumpati, accāsanne kammaṃ karoti, na ca nidhānakusalo hoti. "
msgstr "He attacks unprovoked. He steals everything without exception. He kills a woman. He rapes a girl. He robs a monk. He robs the royal treasury. He works close to home. He’s not skilled at hiding his booty. "

msgctxt "an8.84:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato mahācoro khippaṃ pariyāpajjati, na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti. "
msgstr "A master thief with these eight factors is soon executed, and doesn’t have long to live. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.84:2.1"
msgid "Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato mahācoro na khippaṃ pariyāpajjati, ciraṭṭhitiko hoti. "
msgstr "A master thief with eight factors is not soon executed, and lives long. "

msgctxt "an8.84:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.84:2.3"
msgid "Na appaharantassa paharati, na anavasesaṃ ādiyati, na itthiṃ hanati, na kumāriṃ dūseti, na pabbajitaṃ vilumpati, na rājakosaṃ vilumpati, na accāsanne kammaṃ karoti, nidhānakusalo ca hoti. "
msgstr "He doesn’t attack unprovoked. He doesn’t steal everything without exception. He doesn’t kill a woman. He doesn’t rape a girl. He doesn’t rob a monk. He doesn’t rob the royal treasury. He doesn’t work close to home. He’s skilled at hiding his booty. "

msgctxt "an8.84:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato mahācoro na khippaṃ pariyāpajjati, ciraṭṭhitiko hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A master thief with these eight factors is not soon executed, and lives long.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.84:2.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

